<h2 style="color:#18181b; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 16px;">Subscription cancelled.</h2>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  Hey <%= @user.first_name.presence || @user.username %> —
</p>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  Your Train Like Dubi subscription has been cancelled. You'll keep access until the end of your current billing period
  <% if @subscription.current_period_end.present? %>
    (<strong><%= @subscription.current_period_end.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %></strong>)
  <% end %>
  — after that, your access will expire.
</p>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  Changed your mind? You can resubscribe anytime.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center; margin:0 0 28px;">
  <%= link_to "Resubscribe",
      root_url,
      style: "display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; background-color:#dc2626; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;" %>
</p>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7; margin:0 0 20px;">

<p style="color:#71717a; font-size:13px; margin:0;">
  Questions? Reply to this email or reach us at
  <a href="mailto:support@trainlikedubi.com" style="color:#ef4444; text-decoration:none;">support@trainlikedubi.com</a>.
</p>
